SCHEMA: fluid/burst_event.schema
schema_id: dominium.schema.fluid.burst_event
schema_version: 1.0.0
stability: core

PURPOSE:
- Canonical deterministic RECORD artifact for FLUID catastrophic containment failure.

REQUIRED SHAPE:
record burst_event
  required:
    - schema_version: semver
    - event_id: id
    - target_id: id
    - overpressure_value: number
    - deterministic_fingerprint: sha256
    - extensions: map